<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NIDS - Network Intrusion Detection System</title>
    
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/5bf56866c4.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    
    <!-- Custom Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/homeStyles.css">
    
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero-section::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        .hero-buttons .btn {
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }
        .hero-buttons .btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.9), 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature-box {
            padding: 30px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .feature-box:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.8);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.8), 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        .feature-box i {
            color: #0ff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.7), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        .feature-box h3 {
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7), 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<body>
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Protect Your Network with Advanced Intrusion Detection</h1>
            <p>Stay ahead of cyber threats with real-time analysis and intelligent threat detection.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="/submit" class="btn btn-light">Sign-In</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-light">Sign-Up</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features-section container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-network-wired fa-3x"></i>
                    <h3>AI-Powered Intrusion Detection with Data Heterogeneity</h3>
                    <p>Train ML models (SVM,Decision Trees) with real and SMOTE-generated synthetic data to detect frequent and rare attacks and hence compare their performance .</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt fa-3x"></i>
                    <h3>Adaptive Threat Prevention</h3>
                    <p>Real-time learning and adaptation to evolving cyberattacks, ensuring proactive security measures.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-3x"></i>
                    <h3>Intelligent Network Analysis</h3>
                    <p>Analyzing network behavior and distinguishing between legitimate and malicious activities using AI-driven insights.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 NIDS - All Rights Reserved</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
